ht into the stability of these constrictions and\nan evolutionary trace of deformation modes, beginning with a single-atom\ncontact.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2011 16:56:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-04-07"}
